---
import { siteConfig } from "../config";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="de" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <title>Datenschutzerklärung</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
</head>

<body class="bg-white text-gray-800">
<main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto p-8 sm:p-12">
    <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Datenschutzerklärung</h1>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Hosting</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
        This website is hosted on <strong>GitHub Pages</strong>, a service
        provided by GitHub, Inc., 88 Colin P Kelly Jr St, San Francisco, CA 94107,
        USA.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4">
        When visiting this website, GitHub may process technical information such
        as IP address, date and time of access, browser type, and operating
        system. This data is required for the secure and reliable delivery of the
        website.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Cookies & Tracking</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
        This website does <strong>not</strong> use cookies or tracking tools.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">External Links</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
        This website may contain links to external websites (e.g., GitHub,
        arXiv). I have no control over the content or data processing practices of
        these websites.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
        You have the right to request information about the personal data stored
        about you and to request its correction or deletion in accordance with
        applicable data protection laws.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Contact</h2>
    <p>
        For privacy-related inquiries, please contact:<br />
        <a
                href="mailto:f.rosenthal@tum.de"
                class="underline"
                style={`color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}`}
        >
            f.rosenthal@tum.de
        </a>
    </p>
</main>
</body>
</html>
